      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "是好汉随老父参王见驾，少刻间见万岁，谁是谁非，儿要启奏皇家。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00028",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "臣，姚期见驾，吾皇万岁！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00029",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "姚皇兄你可知罪？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00030",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "臣知罪，不知罪犯何条？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00031",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "今有你三子姚刚，骑马游街，将郭老太师打死。你还言无罪？",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00032",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "郭老太师也有一行大罪。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00033",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "罪犯何条？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00034",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "在府门以外私立三尺禁地，文官下轿，武官离鞍。万岁可曾降旨？",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00035",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "这个……孤王有言在先，未曾降旨。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00036",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "万岁无旨，斩者无亏。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00037",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "好一个“斩者无亏”！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00038",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "绑坏了！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00039",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "吓，殿角下绑的何人？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00040",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "三子姚刚。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00041",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "内侍，快快松绑，不要绑坏孤的少爱卿！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00042",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "太监甲松绑。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00043",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "谢万岁不之恩！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00044",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "非是孤王不斩与你，是孤先前许下“姚不反汉，汉不斩姚”。赐你三千人马，去到湖北枉子城，保定金固牛庄。你父子午门一别，下殿去吧！",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00045",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期",
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "谢万岁！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00046",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "三笑",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈，哈哈，哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00047",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "奴才！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00048",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "万岁爷赦了姚霸林，好似枯木又逢春。手拉姣儿下龙廷，开言叫声姚霸林：此番湖北儿要改性情，儿不要提刀乱杀人！",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00049",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "儿来看。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00050",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "看什么？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00051",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "为父的年迈苍苍白如银，姚刚，我的儿吓！好一似瓦上霜、风前灯，能过几春？",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00052",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00053",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹落泪儿悲伤，点点珠泪洒胸膛。在朝为官有什么好？一点不到有损伤！倒不如写上辞王表，告职回乡乐安康。在午门辞别生身父，回府去拜上老萱堂。",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00054",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹，我父，爹爹吓！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00055",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "姚刚下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00056",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "三叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "姚刚，霸林，哎吓我的儿吓！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00057",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "金殿去了姚霸林，父子们相逢万不能。转过金阶梧桐树，告职回乡乐安宁。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00058",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "臣启见万岁！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00059",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "吓，姚皇兄为何去而复返？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00060",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "臣启万岁：臣要告职归林。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00061",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "皇兄告职，寡人怎样舍得？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00062",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "要臣在朝伴驾，依臣一件。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00063",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "哪一件？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00064",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "万岁戒酒百日，老臣方能在朝伴驾。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00065",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "只要皇兄在朝，慢说戒酒百日，就是周年半岁，又待何妨？内侍，将姚皇兄扶起！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00066",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "太监甲扶姚期。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00067",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "谢万岁！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00068",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "姚皇兄休得要告职还乡，龙书案听寡人细说端详：你本是坐朝中开国良将，叫寡人怎舍得架海金梁？",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00069",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "非是臣在金殿告职还乡，老姚期有一本启奏吾王：小姚刚打死了太师命丧，怕的是郭娘娘陷害忠良。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006018_e00070",
      "play_id": "01006018",
      "scene_id": "01006018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "孤离了龙书案把话来讲，君臣们站金阙细谈衷肠：昔日里老王爷龙归海葬，那时节孤年幼不能承当。那王莽将玉殿自行执掌，将孤王赶出都流落他乡。甲子年那王莽曾开科场，众举子内其中也有孤王。孤一心放冷箭射死王莽，又谁知那一箭不曾带伤。那王莽中了那岑彭貌相，科场内怒走了马武子章。城墙上提反诗险把命丧，孤与那邓先生到卿的宝庄。鬼神庄兴皇乡住了一乡，老皇兄曾言道上有高堂。老伯母窗台外偷听话讲，行至在厨房下自尽悬梁。老皇兄要守孝三年制丧，天下人俱挂孝方称心肠。六月天霎时间曾把雪降，老皇兄，三年孝改三月，三月孝改三日，三日孝改三时，三年、三月、三日、三时，三刻不满，扶保孤王。孤念你开国臣曾把江闯，孤念你秉忠心扶保家邦。孤念你一杆枪东征西讨，孤念你每年间，东挡西除，马不停蹄，血战疆场，到如今你还是扶保孤王！孤念你三个子把两子来丧，孤念你只剩下一子姚刚。孤念你两鬓苍苍如同霜降，孤念你风前灯瓦上之霜。后宫院孤赐你玉宴琼浆，王戒酒你陪酒又待何妨？君臣们站金阙细说相让，叫一声姚皇兄，姚子匡，伴驾王，孤的爱卿，你那里放宽心，大着胆，一步一步随定了孤王！",
